  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000078",
    "sentence": "在職有治方，為邊民悅服。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000079",
    "sentence": "大寧中，卒於膠州刺史。",
    "entities": [
