        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "因逃還鄉",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 10,
        "end": 14
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000101",
    "sentence": "高祖以㥄本預義旗，復其黃門。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000102",
    "sentence": "天平初，為侍讀，監典書。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000103",
    "sentence": "尋除徐州刺史，給廣宗部曲三百、清河部曲千人。",
