  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000128",
    "sentence": "尋有別勑，斬馮於都市。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000129",
    "sentence": "㥄以疾卒獄中，年六十一。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000130",
    "sentence": "㥄歷覽群書，兼有詞藻，自中興立後，迄於武帝，詔誥表檄，多㥄所為。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000131",
    "sentence": "然率性豪侈，溺於財色，諸弟之間，不能盡雍穆之美，世論以此譏之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000132",
    "sentence": "㥄素與魏收不協，收既專典國史，㥄恐被惡言，乃悅之曰：「昔有班固，今則魏子。」收笑而憾不釋。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000133",
    "sentence": "子瞻嗣。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000134",
    "sentence": "瞻字彥通，聰明強學，有文情，善容止，神采嶷然，言不妄發。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000135",
    "sentence": "年十五，刺史高昂召署主簿，清河公岳辟開府西閣祭酒。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "刺史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 6
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000136",
    "sentence": "崔暹為中尉，啟除御史，以才望見收，非其好也。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 8,
        "end": 10
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000137",
    "sentence": "高祖入朝，還晉陽，被召與北海王晞陪從，俱為諸子賓友。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000138",
    "sentence": "仍為相府中兵參軍，轉主簿。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000139",
    "sentence": "世宗崩，秘未發喪，顯祖命瞻兼相府司馬使鄴。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "司馬",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 16,
        "end": 18
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000140",
    "sentence": "魏孝靜帝以人日登雲龍門，其父㥄侍宴，又敕瞻令近御坐，亦有應詔詩，問邢卲等曰：「此詩何如其父？」咸云：「㥄博雅弘麗，瞻氣調清新，並詩人之冠。」宴罷，共嗟賞之，咸云：「今日之讌，併為崔瞻父子。」",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000141",
    "sentence": "天保初，兼幷省吏部郎中。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000142",
    "sentence": "尋丁憂，起為司徒屬。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000143",
    "sentence": "楊愔欲引瞻為中書侍郎。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "侍郎",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 8,
        "end": 10
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000144",
    "sentence": "時盧思道直中書省，因問思道曰：「我此日多務，都不見崔瞻文藻，卿與其親通，理當相悉。」思道答曰：「崔瞻文詞之美，實有可稱，但舉世重其風流，所以才華見沒。」愔云：「此言有理。」便奏用之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000145",
    "sentence": "事既施行。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000146",
    "sentence": "愔又曰：「昔裴瓚晉世為中書郎，神情高邁，每於禁門出入，宿衛者肅然動容。崔生堂堂之貌，亦當無愧裴子。」",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000147",
    "sentence": "皇建元年 ，除給事黃門侍郎。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "侍郎",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 11,
        "end": 13
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000148",
    "sentence": "與趙郡李概為莫逆之友。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "與趙郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 3
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000149",
    "sentence": "概將東還，瞻遺之書曰：「仗氣使酒，我之常弊，詆訶指切，在卿尤甚。足下告歸，吾於何聞過也？」瞻患氣，兼性遲重，雖居二省，竟不堪敷奏。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000150",
    "sentence": "加征虜將軍，除清河邑中正。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "將軍",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 3,
        "end": 5
      },
      {
        "text": "除清河邑",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 10
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000151",
    "sentence": "肅宗踐祚，皇太子就傅受業，詔除太子中庶子，徵赴晉陽。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 8
      },
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 15,
        "end": 17
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000152",
    "sentence": "勑專在東宮，調護講讀，及進退禮度，皆歸委焉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000153",
    "sentence": "太子納妃斛律氏，勑瞻與鴻臚崔劼撰定婚禮儀注。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000154",
    "sentence": "仍面受別旨曰：「雖有舊事，恐未盡善，可好定此儀，以為後式。」",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000155",
    "sentence": "大寧元年，除衛尉少卿，尋兼散騎常侍，聘陳使主。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "元年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000156",
    "sentence": "瞻詞韻溫雅，南人大相欽服，乃言：「常侍前朝通好之日，何意不來？」其見重如此。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000157",
    "sentence": "還除太常少卿，加冠軍將軍，轉尚書吏部郎中。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "將軍",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 10,
        "end": 12
      },
      {
        "text": "尚書",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 14,
        "end": 16
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000158",
    "sentence": "因患急十餘日。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000159",
    "sentence": "舊式，百日不上解官，吏部尚書尉瑾性褊急，以瞻舉指舒緩，曹務繁劇，遂附驛奏聞，因而被代。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "尚書",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 12,
        "end": 14
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000160",
    "sentence": "瞻遂免歸鄉里。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "瞻遂免歸鄉",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 5
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000161",
    "sentence": "天統末，加驃騎大將軍，就拜銀青光祿大夫。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "大將軍",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 7,
        "end": 10
      },
      {
        "text": "大夫",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 17,
        "end": 19
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000162",
    "sentence": "武平三年 卒，時年五十四。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "三年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000163",
    "sentence": "贈使持節、都督濟州軍事、大理卿、刺史，諡曰文。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "都督濟州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 9
      },
      {
        "text": "刺史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 16,
        "end": 18
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000164",
    "sentence": "瞻性簡傲，以才地自矜，所與周旋，皆一時名望。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000165",
    "sentence": "在御史臺，恒於宅中送食，備盡珍羞，別室獨飡，處之自若。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 1,
        "end": 3
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000166",
    "sentence": "有一河東人士姓裴，亦為御史，伺瞻食，便往造焉。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 11,
        "end": 13
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000167",
    "sentence": "瞻不與交言，又不命匕筯。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000168",
    "sentence": "裴坐觀瞻食罷而退。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000169",
    "sentence": "明日，裴自攜匕筯，恣情飲噉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000170",
    "sentence": "瞻方謂裴云：「我初不喚君食，亦不共君語，君遂能不拘小節。昔劉毅在京口，冒請鵝炙，豈亦異於是乎？君定名士。」於是每與之同食。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000171",
    "sentence": "㥄昆季仲文，有學尚，魏高陽太守、清河內史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太守",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 13,
        "end": 15
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000172",
    "sentence": "興和中，為丞相掾。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "丞相",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 7
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000173",
    "sentence": "沙苑之敗，仲文持馬尾以渡河，波中乍沒乍出。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000174",
    "sentence": "高祖望見曰：「崔掾也。」遽遣船赴接。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000175",
    "sentence": "既濟，勞之曰：「卿為親為君，不顧萬死，可謂家之孝子，國之忠臣。」加中軍將軍。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "將軍",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 35,
        "end": 37
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000176",
    "sentence": "天保初，拜散騎常侍、光祿大夫。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "大夫",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 12,
        "end": 14
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000177",
    "sentence": "七年卒，年六十。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "七年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000178",
    "sentence": "子偃，武平中，歷太子洗馬、尚書郎。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 8,
        "end": 10
      },
      {
        "text": "尚書",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 13,
        "end": 15
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000179",
    "sentence": "偃弟儦，學識有才思，風調甚高。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000180",
    "sentence": "武平中，瑯琊王大司馬中兵參軍。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "司馬",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 8,
        "end": 10
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000181",
    "sentence": "參定五禮，待詔文林館。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000182",
    "sentence": "隋仁壽中，卒於通直散騎常侍。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000183",
    "sentence": "叔仁，魏潁州刺史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "魏潁州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 3,
        "end": 6
      },
      {
        "text": "刺史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 8
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000184",
    "sentence": "子彥武，有識用，朝歌令。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000185",
    "sentence": "隋開皇初，魏州刺史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "魏州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "刺史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 7,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000186",
    "sentence": "子侃，魏末兼通直常侍，聘梁使。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "魏",
        "label": "ORG",
        "start": 3,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000187",
    "sentence": "子極，武平初太子僕，卒於武德郡守。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 8
      },
      {
        "text": "卒於武德郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 10,
        "end": 15
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000188",
    "sentence": "子聿，魏東莞太守。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太守",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 8
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000189",
    "sentence": "子約，司空祭酒。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000190",
    "sentence": "㥄族叔景鳳，字鸞叔，㥄五世祖逞玄孫也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000191",
    "sentence": "景鳳涉學，以醫術知名。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000192",
    "sentence": "魏尚藥典御，天保中譙州刺史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "天保中譙州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 11
      },
      {
        "text": "刺史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 11,
        "end": 13
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000193",
    "sentence": "景鳳兄景哲，魏太中大夫、司徒長史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "大夫",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 9,
        "end": 11
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000194",
    "sentence": "子國，字法峻，幼好學，泛覽經傳，多伎藝，尤工相術。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_023_000195",
    "sentence": "天保初尚藥典御，乾明拜高陽郡太守、太子家令，武平假儀同三司，卒於鴻臚卿。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "乾明拜高陽郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 8,
        "end": 14
      },
      {
